name: Cosmic Gate
cleanBio: GRAMMY Â® nominated trance legends Cosmic Gate aka Nic Chagall and Bossi have proved to be a matchless musical union. The last 20 years set them on the course to becoming Germany's most enduringly successful electronic music duo. Smashing the biggest festivals and road-blocking clubs worldwide, got them highest climber on DJ Mag's Top 100 chart and racked up plentiful other awards & nominations along the way. Numerous Singles like 'am2pm', 'Fall Into You' and 'Falling Back', countless Remixes and 11 Artist Albums, including scene-defining classics like 'Be Your Sound', 'Fire Wire' and 'Exploration of Space' (20 million Spotify streams), their star on dance music's walk of fame has long since been laid.
